            <li><strong>Upgradeability:</strong> Proxy patterns allowing arbitrary code changes</li>
            <li><strong>Parameter Manipulation:</strong> Dynamic fee structures and rate modifications</li>
            <li><strong>Emergency Withdrawals:</strong> Hidden functions enabling fund extraction</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>1.2 Our Solution</h3>
